{"title":"Template使用","uid":"f47763623b3b8805dadf294b2f1115a1","slug":"template使用","date":"2023-01-22T06:07:17.679Z","updated":"2023-01-24T04:33:43.711Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/template使用.json","keywords":null,"cover":"http://cn.bing.com/hpwp/fa0352abc70decbca85c0c541bd96c45","content":"<h3 id=\"图片\"><a href=\"#图片\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"图片\"></a>图片</h3><p>得到随机图片, 可设置大小 ,关键字!<br>写日记的模板可用👉<br>需求: </p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p> 如果可以得到文中的标签, 那么就可以直接渲染到tags标签上, 而且还可以搜索随机图片👉</p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"示例\"><a href=\"#示例\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"示例\"></a>示例</h3><h4 id=\"打开控制台\"><a href=\"#打开控制台\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"打开控制台\"></a>打开控制台</h4><p><code>CTRL+shift+i</code> 可以进行调试, 类似网站…<br><img src=\"images/Pasted%20image%2020230122163237.png\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"文章中标签与yml中tags-同步\"><a href=\"#文章中标签与yml中tags-同步\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"文章中标签与yml中tags 同步\"></a>文章中标签与yml中<code>tags</code> 同步</h4><p>在<code>插件市场</code> 下载 <code>Linter</code><br><img src=\"images/Pasted%20image%2020230122165258.png\"><br>再轻松配置一下就可实现了<br><img src=\"images/Pasted%20image%2020230122165943.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"images/Pasted%20image%2020230122165954.png\"></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p> ps: 这是从github中的<a href=\"https://github.com/SilentVoid13/Templater/discussions/610\">讨论</a>看到的, 感谢那位大佬!<br><img src=\"images/Pasted%20image%2020230122165731.png\"><br>所以说得到了一个经验: 当有需求时, 可以多去GitHub上搜搜相关的库, 再去讨论里面逛逛, 相信会有所收获的! #经验 </p></blockquote>\n<h4 id=\"显示图片-控制图片大小\"><a href=\"#显示图片-控制图片大小\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"显示图片(控制图片大小)\"></a>显示图片(控制图片大小)</h4><p>比如我想显示 key为”<strong>technology</strong>“ 的图片👈 随机 可以这么写: 还可以设置图片的大小: 200x200 也可以设置多个关键字, 用<code>,</code> 分隔即可<br>&lt;% tp.web.random_picture(“”, “technology”) %&gt; 如图👇<br><img src=\"images/Pasted%20image%2020230122164713.png\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"quickadd-马上打开新建文件\"><a href=\"#quickadd-马上打开新建文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"quickadd 马上打开新建文件\"></a>quickadd 马上打开新建文件</h4><p>打开quickadd设置, 之后配置如下两项就行了👇<br><img src=\"images/Pasted%20image%2020230122171926.png\"><br>成功!</p>\n<h4 id=\"写日记\"><a href=\"#写日记\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"写日记\"></a>写日记</h4>","text":"图片得到随机图片, 可设置大小 ,关键字!写日记的模板可用👉需求: 如果可以得到文中的标签, 那么就可以直接渲染到tags标签上, 而且还可以搜索随机图片👉 示例打开控制台CTRL+shift+i 可以进行调试, 类似网站… 文章中标签与yml中tags 同步在插件市场 下载 L...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":473,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"ob/插件","slug":"ob-插件","count":2,"path":"api/categories/ob-插件.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"ob","slug":"ob","count":5,"path":"api/tags/ob.json"},{"name":"template","slug":"template","count":1,"path":"api/tags/template.json"},{"name":"经验","sl